{"tid":1186391,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"$1.7億迪士尼碼頭 半荒廢 電任偷","createTime":"2019-06-05T01:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T13:09:09.000Z","uid":56881,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"49056d0f878ebab7fe5b00b900431d6814c64254","tid":1186391,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T01:48:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/1-7%E5%84%84%E8%BF%AA%E5%A3%AB%E5%B0%BC%E7%A2%BC%E9%A0%AD-%E5%8D%8A%E8%8D%92%E5%BB%A2-%E9%9B%BB%E4%BB%BB%E5%81%B7-214500804.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F1-7%25E5%2584%2584%25E8%25BF%25AA%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E9%25A0%25AD-%25E5%258D%258A%25E8%258D%2592%25E5%25BB%25A2-%25E9%259B%25BB%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%2581%25B7-214500804.html&d=bqe6r6CGoyJNILHzVVCKL36wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=cfcf5c07\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/1-7%E5%84%84%E8%BF%AA%E5%A3%AB%E5%B0%BC%E7%A2%BC%E9%A0%AD-%E5%8D%8A%E8%8D%92%E5%BB%A2-%E9%9B%BB%E4%BB%BB%E5%81%B7-214500804.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/IYtqvV5NonbKSCrGBz5g4w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/e30257b8052f9130618607e9eb13d43f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FIYtqvV5NonbKSCrGBz5g4w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Fe30257b8052f9130618607e9eb13d43f&h=0e081424&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日為釣墨魚旺季，夜間有不少釣友闖入碼頭位置垂釣。<br />\n<br />\n景點碼頭如同荒廢，建造管理浪費公帑。大嶼山迪士尼碼頭耗資近一億七千萬元，每日只有一班觀光航班，周末亦人流稀疏，其中一邊大堂更於去年超強颱風山竹襲港期間飽受摧殘，至今仍蓉蓉爛爛，暫停開放；近日更疑有人直闖險地，偷電釣墨魚。大埔海濱公園內碼頭雖曾舉辦墟市，亦已慘變廢墟，毗鄰的釣魚區更無人問津。立法會議員狠批昂貴碼頭吸引力低，望政府吸取教訓，興建遊客設施前應充分諮詢評估，並盡快檢視情況，免倒錢落海。<br />\n<br />\n觀光遊每日僅一班嘥公帑<br />\n<br />\n耗資近一億七千萬元公帑興建的迪士尼碼頭於○五年啟用，屬迪士尼樂園首批完成的基建項目，惟啟用後政府曾兩度公開招標開辦航線，惜乏人問津，現時僅由天星小輪營運每日一班觀光遊航班，於上午十一時由尖沙咀天星碼頭開出，而中午十二時十五分則由迪士尼碼頭再駛回尖沙咀，途經青馬大橋等景點，但遊人疏落。本報記者周末發現，整艘觀光輪只有約三、四十人，大多是內地遊客，其中十多名遊客落船後未有再上船。<br />\n<br />\n該碼頭是以維多利亞風格建設，原來裝修別具特色，惟十四年來遊客稀少，接待遊客的設施已告停用，兩個售票處停用失修，顯得格外荒涼。其中東側大堂去年受山竹吹襲影響，大閘掛上暫停開放橫額，玻璃鋪滿灰塵，天花燈的燈槽電線掉落，大型鐵欄塌下仍未清理，碼頭底亦已搭建維修。<br />\n<br />\n議員轟政府無充分諮詢<br />\n<br />\n「橫掂錢都嘥咗，對我哋嚟講都係一件好事嘅！」碼頭日夜都甚少有船泊岸，近年成為釣魚勝地，有釣魚客直指魚獲甚豐，假日有不少人來航拍或拍照打卡等，均非光顧樂園的遊人，他笑稱公帑已浪費，能吸引人釣魚亦有價值。近日為釣墨魚旺季，已停用的東側大堂及靠近燈塔位置更吸引不少人釣墨魚，甚至有人涉闖入荒廢碼頭偷電接駁大光燈。<br />\n<br />\n離島區議員容詠嫦直指，從未見過有人使用該碼頭，「啲遊客去迪士尼都係搭港鐵，邊會搭船？」她表示，一、兩年前曾有區內人士反映，希望增設周末早上來往中環、迪士尼碼頭與愉景灣的班次，以吸引遊客到愉景灣食肆消費，可惜最終因迪士尼碼頭日久失修，導致船隻未能停泊，航班建議亦不了了之。她直斥，政府豪花公帑興建碼頭，使用量奇低，實在浪費，又批評政府未有以積極態度去改善情況，「如果佢想做，呢十四年就一早做咗喇！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.dicazcLbLgQp6qNVbw39w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/3226a3f569ae151ea769664d480e73bc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F.dicazcLbLgQp6qNVbw39w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F3226a3f569ae151ea769664d480e73bc&h=8a0fbd79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n東側大堂有不少電掣位，近日疑有釣友偷電。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/yviO_piXhGzWejXF72Tilw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/3a30bd8dbaf6f21910f2ff5bd92e59a0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FyviO_piXhGzWejXF72Tilw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F3a30bd8dbaf6f21910f2ff5bd92e59a0&h=d3fc2257&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n迪士尼碼頭東側大堂已封閉，相關告示指因受颱風破壞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/JLFilXcL4ZzUG3SGfNtmjw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/739b60ba6c210415e6a0b48719e7d9df\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FJLFilXcL4ZzUG3SGfNtmjw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F739b60ba6c210415e6a0b48719e7d9df&h=623f85f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n碼頭內其中一個售票處已停用，玻璃鋪滿灰塵。<br />\n<br />\n政府做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又有電又大地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb33b98fa3dd80503ed18b3a2c3ba1546533864","tid":1186391,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T01:50:52.000Z","msg":"呢個位不嬲好撚靜<br />\n就算用錢整返好都冇人會去"},{"pid":"7e9492e4cfbac22f7e0318f69d08dce71e8254c6","tid":1186391,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T01:53:33.000Z","msg":"正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ac91ee1da6eaf7ee09ff0f1502594cbe993126","tid":1186391,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adb33b98fa3dd80503ed18b3a2c3ba1546533864","tid":1186391,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T01:50:52.000Z","msg":"呢個位不嬲好撚靜<br />\n就算用錢整返好都冇人會去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T01:54:23.000Z","msg":"冇船緊係靜"},{"pid":"a5030d8e74d8e1e75a0929d66fddf252b60057b3","tid":1186391,"uid":33868,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"53ac91ee1da6eaf7ee09ff0f1502594cbe993126","tid":1186391,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adb33b98fa3dd80503ed18b3a2c3ba1546533864","tid":1186391,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T01:50:52.000Z","msg":"呢個位不嬲好撚靜<br />\n就算用錢整返好都冇人會去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T01:54:23.000Z","msg":"冇船緊係靜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T01:55:11.000Z","msg":"有船都唔會有人坐<br />\n迪士尼有鐵路<br />\n仲要個碼頭唔近樂園入口"},{"pid":"ad64eb6fbf9177390e9ff97013d006cc9bc87176","tid":1186391,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5030d8e7